optimize (1.0.7-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix false deb-src warning when .sources files exist but
    deb-src is configured in legacy sources.list
  * Also check /etc/apt/sources.list and .list files before
    concluding deb-src is not enabled
  * Suppress dpkg-query errors and implement fallbacks (linux-image, apt-cache, linux)
    for better kernel source package resolution
  * Improve .config detection (checks /boot, /proc/config.gz, falls back to defconfig)
  * Enhance kernel build process resilience by properly handling non-fatal errors
  * Add automatic dependency resolution with apt-get build-dep

 -- helton <chileno.brasil@gmail.com>  Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:00:00 -0300

optimize (1.0.6-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Update installation method to use dpkg --force-overwrite and
    automatically fix broken dependencies.
  * Implement --kernel optimization flag using localmodconfig and
    KCFLAGS
  * Update README to document the --kernel parameter
  * Fix --kernel source package detection by querying linux-headers
    instead of linux-image
  * Fix make localmodconfig pipefail crash
  * Fix kernel build: Add libdw-dev dependency and use --set-str for
    trust keys

